FA SKY DODGE

Upload the contents of this folder to your GitHub repository.
For GitHub Pages:
1. Create or open a repository.
2. Upload index.html.
3. In Settings > Pages, set the source branch.
4. Open the published URL.

Controls
- PC: Arrow keys / A D
- Mobile: Touch buttons at the bottom
- Pause: P or Space or Pause button
- Fullscreen: button on start screen or key F

All records are stored locally in the browser.
